Last change: 04 Apr 2005


CLIP-UI
-------
 - Spreadsheet widget 
 - Set slot functions for window open, activation, close
 + Move to driver gdk_ColorParse() function from uicolor.prg
 + Additional parameter 'signal' in method setAction()
 - New widgets:
   + UILayout (fixed positions of widgets)
   + UIRadioButton
   + UIProgressBar
   + UISlider
   - UIChoice (for date(+), number, file(+), color(+), form)
     + for date picking see http://gtk.org/tutorial2.0/sec-calendar.html
   - UIIconView
   - UITab
   - UIWizard
   - UIList
 + Program activation of UIChildWindow
 + New classes for UITable/UITree nodes
 - DnD methods for UITable/UITree
 - Deletion of widget from comtainers
 - Disallow editing in UIComboBox field
 - Using ID in UIComboBox
 - Possible security hole in array interpretation ("{|| {"+array_string+"} }")
 - gtk_ScrolledWindowNew() make child widget too small
 - sent command line parameters to gtk_Init()
 - Default selection needed for UIComboBox in forms
 - usablity issues for UISlider: value should be step multiple, step indication under slider
 - icons for UIChildWindow
 - wrong setFocus() behaviour for widgets in UIChildWindow/UIDocument
 - UIEditDate should display calendar in popup window
 - UIEditDate: date should be selected by keyboard
 + Modal dialogs for select file name, color or date
 
GTK2 driver
-----------
 + Set style: gtk_WidgetModifyFG() gtk_WidgetModifyBG(), gtk_WidgetModifyFont()...
 - Input numero sign on typographic quotes
 + Migrate UIComboBox to gtk_ComboBox
 
Documentation
-------------
 - separate section "CLIP-UI" in CLIP documentation 
 - XFL format description
 + UISlider class
 + UIChildWindow:setCaption(), caption attribute for all window classes
 + param passed to UIWorkSpace()
 - list support (and any other Docbook tags) in .txt class/funcs description files
 - UIDriver class
 - full attribute list of window classes
 
